  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is a combination of outpatient and inpatient monitoring. During the 27-day
      inpatient portion of the study, the individual's sleep-wake schedule will be varied daily.
      Volunteers will be randomized to a regular or irregular inpatient schedule.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
